Finance::YahooJPN::QuoteHist version 0.04
=========================================

 This module provides you functions to fetch historical quotes
 of Japanese stock markets from Yahoo-Japan-Finance.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

 This module and the test script requires internet connection.
 And the test script will take several minutes to progress.

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.
 And,
 this module requires these other modules and libraries:

   LWP::Simple

